---
import CustomImage from '@/components/CustomImage'
import ImageCarousel from '@/components/ImageCarousel'
import CardCarousel from '@/components/CardCarousel'
import StickyHeader from '@/components/StickyHeader'
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout'

const SITE_TITLE = 'SenCar 6'
---

<BaseLayout title={SITE_TITLE}>
	<div>
		<h1 class='title text-6xl font-bold'>{SITE_TITLE}</h1>
		<h2 class='text-3xl font-medium mt-4 mb-10'>Superpowered</h2>
		<CustomImage
			imagePath='/src/assets/images/software/sencar-6/hero.jpg'
			altText='SenCar 6, the new superpowered car OS, in all its glory'
		/>

		<article class='prose prose-xl dark:prose-invert w-full max-w-none mt-8'>
			<h2 class='text-4xl font-bold mt-10'>Superpowered</h2>
			<p>
				SenCar 6 is the sequel to the revolutionary SenCar 5, bringing even more advanced features
				and enhanced performance to your driving experience.
			</p>
			<p>
				SenCar is our incredible car operating system, designed to make driving easier, safer, and
				more enjoyable. It features gorgeous interfaces, intuitive controls, and seamless
				integration with your vehicle's hardware.
			</p>
			<h2 class='text-4xl font-bold mt-10'>What's new in SenCar 6</h2>
			<CardCarousel>
				<div class='rounded-3xl bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 text-center'>
					<h4 class='text-xl font-bold mb-2'>Four New Dashboards</h4>
					<p class='text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300'>
						SenCar 6 lets you choose from four stunning dashboard layouts, each designed with
						EV-first iconography and optimized for different driving styles. Whether you prefer a
						classic look or a modern interface, there's a dashboard for you.
					</p>
					<CustomImage
						imagePath='/src/assets/images/software/sencar-6/aita_all_dash.jpg'
						altText='The different dashboard themes and layouts'
					/>
				</div>
				<div class='rounded-3xl bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 text-center'>
					<h4 class='text-xl font-bold mb-2'>Major Optimizations</h4>
					<p class='text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300'>
						30% performance boost across the board, with faster response times, smoother animations,
						and improved stability. SenCar 6 is optimized to run efficiently on a wide range of
						hardware, ensuring a seamless experience for all users.
					</p>
					<CustomImage
						imagePath='/src/assets/images/software/sencar-6/settings.jpg'
						altText='Settings and customization options for the dashboard'
					/>
				</div>
				<div class='rounded-3xl bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 text-center'>
					<h4 class='text-xl font-bold mb-2'>Enhanced Customization</h4>
					<p class='text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300'>
						More ways to make SenCar your own. New RGB modes, 7 great color themes, dark mode, and
						custom hues all let you customize your driving experience to match your style and
						preferences.
					</p>
					<CustomImage
						imagePath='/src/assets/images/software/sencar-6/colors.jpg'
						altText='Customizable color themes for the dashboard'
					/>
				</div>
				<div class='rounded-3xl bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 text-center'>
					<h4 class='text-xl font-bold mb-2'>Safer</h4>
					<p class='text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300'>
						Advanced driver assistance systems, automatic emergency braking, and enhanced
						connectivity options make SenCar 6 safer than ever.
					</p>
					<CustomImage
						imagePath='/src/assets/images/software/sencar-6/aeb.jpg'
						altText='Advanced driver assistance systems and enhanced connectivity options'
					/>
				</div>
				<div class='rounded-3xl bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 text-center'>
					<h4 class='text-xl font-bold mb-2'>Autopilot</h4>
					<p class='text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300'>
						Radar Autopilot [BETA] gives you hands-free driving on highways and in traffic, with
						advanced sensors and AI algorithms that make multiplayer driving easier than ever.
					</p>
					<CustomImage
						imagePath='/src/assets/images/software/sencar-6/autopilot.png'
						altText='Radar Autopilot [BETA] in action'
					/>
				</div>
			</CardCarousel>

			<h2 class='text-4xl font-bold mt-16'>A Massive Performance Leap</h2>
			<p>
				Performance has always been a priority for SenCar, but SenCar 6 takes it to an entirely new
				level. On high-end systems, you can expect a 20–30% performance increase across the board -
				faster response times, smoother animations, and a more fluid overall experience. But the
				real story is on lower-end hardware: SenCar 6 delivers upwards of a 60% performance increase
				on low-end systems, meaning drivers who previously experienced lag or frame drops can now
				enjoy a buttery-smooth interface just like everyone else.
			</p>
			<p>
				This wasn't achieved through a single silver bullet, but through dozens of targeted
				optimizations across every subsystem - from rendering pipelines to app logic. Several apps
				received particularly significant overhauls: the map experience has been completely
				re-engineered for speed and clarity, the Weather app runs more efficiently than ever, and
				Settings has been rebuilt to load and respond instantly.
			</p>
			<p>
				On top of the core improvements, we've introduced two powerful new tools to help you squeeze
				even more performance out of SenCar 6. The new Gradient Resolution slider lets you dial back
				the visual fidelity of gradient effects, giving you granular control over the balance
				between beauty and performance. And the new Multiplayer Mode automatically disables screens
				that aren't being actively used, dramatically cutting down on unnecessary processing - a
				game-changer for multiplayer sessions where every frame counts.
			</p>
			<p>
				Speaking of multiplayer, SenCar 6 also includes dedicated work to reduce desync in
				multiplayer sessions, alongside fixes for dozens of bugs reported by the community. SenCar 6
				is the most polished, most performant version of SenCar we've ever shipped.
			</p>

			<h2 class='text-4xl font-bold mt-16'>Customization Like Never Before</h2>
			<p>
				SenCar has always let you make your car your own, but SenCar 6 redefines what that means.
				The new color system is the most expressive yet - choose from 7 great color themes as your
				base, then fine-tune with a brand-new Hue slider to dial in exactly the right shade for you,
				your mood, or the moment. Whether you want a crisp Arctic blue, a deep passionate red, or
				something entirely unique, the combination of themes and hue adjustment means the
				possibilities are practically endless.
			</p>
			<p>
				And if static colors aren't enough, SenCar 6 introduces new RGB and Rave Modes - not just
				for the screen, but for the interior dome light too. Watch your cabin pulse and shift
				through the full spectrum, turning every drive into something a little more special. Paired
				with the new Dark Mode and automatic headlights, SenCar 6's lighting system is more dynamic,
				more atmospheric, and more alive than ever.
			</p>

			<h2 class='text-4xl font-bold mt-16'>Four Stunning Dashboards</h2>
			<p>
				SenCar 6 ships with four distinct dashboard layouts, each a completely different take on how
				to present your driving information - and every single one comes with both EV and diesel
				variants.
			</p>
			<ul class='list-disc pl-6 space-y-4 mt-4'>
				<li>
					SenCar 6 - The flagship layout of this generation. A clean, flattened UI that retains the
					map but strips away everything non-essential, letting you focus entirely on the road
					ahead. Minimal, modern, and purposefully undistracting.
				</li>
				<li>
					SenCar 5 - The classic we know and love, now available as one of four choices. Gorgeous
					analog-inspired dials, the map front-and-center, and that timeless look that made SenCar
					famous. For those who know what they like.
				</li>
				<li>
					Round - A fresh take on information display, using circular gauges to present your speed,
					battery, and more in a cohesive and satisfying arrangement. Sporty, bold, and instantly
					readable.
				</li>
				<li>
					Modern - The most visually striking of the four. Beautiful gradient lines flow across the
					screen to convey your speed, motor throttle, battery level, and heading in a package
					that's as much art as it is instrument.
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p class='mt-4'>
				Combined with the deep color customization options, the sheer number of possible
				configurations makes Aita with SenCar 6 by far the most customizable vehicle we've ever
				made, and one of the most customizable cars in all of Stormworks. And through all of it,
				SenCar 6 remains intuitive - a new sleek startup requires only a single tap on the
				dashboard, and classic PRND gear shifting keeps things familiar.
			</p>

			<h2 class='text-4xl font-bold mt-16'>Apps Built for Drivers</h2>
			<p>
				SenCar 6 brings meaningful upgrades to the app suite that make everyday driving genuinely
				better. The redesigned map experience is faster, cleaner, and easier to navigate at a
				glance. The all-new EV-specific Info app gives electric vehicle drivers dedicated real-time
				data about their powertrain, battery health, and energy consumption - information that was
				previously scattered or absent, now presented in one focused place.
			</p>
			<p>
				The Weather app has been substantially optimized and now loads faster and updates more
				reliably. Settings has been rebuilt from the ground up to be snappier and more logically
				organized, making it easier than ever to configure SenCar exactly how you want it.
			</p>

			<h2 class='text-4xl font-bold mt-16'>Autopilot: Hands-Free Driving</h2>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/software/sencar-6/radar.jpg'
				altText='Radar Autopilot in action on a highway'
			/>
			<p class='mt-6'>
				One of the crown jewels of SenCar 6 is the all-new Autopilot system. This isn't just cruise
				control - SenCar 6 offers two distinct modes for assisted driving.
			</p>
			<p>
				Classic Cruise Control maintains your set speed automatically, just as you'd expect. Radar
				Autopilot [BETA] uses a radar sensor mounted at the front of the car to detect the vehicle
				ahead of you and follow it autonomously. Full control of the throttle, brakes, and steering
				means the car genuinely drives itself, adjusting speed to match traffic and keeping you
				centered in your lane.
			</p>
			<p>
				Long drives in multiplayer - once a test of endurance and focus - are now something entirely
				different. Enable Autopilot, sit back, and let SenCar take the wheel. It makes those long
				highway stretches feel effortless and, honestly, a little magical.
			</p>

			<h2 class='text-4xl font-bold mt-16'>Safer Than Ever</h2>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/software/sencar-6/aeb.jpg'
				altText='Automatic emergency braking system display'
			/>
			<p class='mt-6'>
				Safety has received significant attention in SenCar 6. Automatic Emergency Braking (AEB)
				monitors the road ahead and intervenes if a collision is imminent, applying the brakes
				faster than any human reaction time could manage. A new dead man's switch ensures the car
				responds appropriately if the driver becomes unresponsive, adding a critical safety net for
				long drives.
			</p>
			<p>
				And for multiplayer, SenCar 6 introduces radio key locking - a dedicated radio key system
				that lets you lock your car, ensuring only you can get in and drive it. No more coming back
				to find someone's taken your Aita for a joyride.
			</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
	import { animate } from 'motion'
	const showAnimations = localStorage.getItem('animations') === 'true'

	if (showAnimations) {
		animate(
			'.title',
			{ y: [80, 0], opacity: [0, 1] },
			{
				duration: 2.5,
				opacity: { duration: 3 },

				offset: [0, 0.55, 0.75]
			}
		)
	}
</script>
